-- Total Kenya Appoints Vovk as Managing Director After Majekodunmi Resigns
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-09-20T05:53:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/total-kenya-appoints-vovk-as-managing-director-after-majekodunmi-resigns.html

          
          
             Total Kenya Ltd. said it appointed
Alexis Vovk as managing director after Olumuyiwa Majekodunmi
resigned amid a series of board changes approved at a Sept. 16
meeting, according to an e-mailed statement today from the
Nairobi Stock Exchange.  
          
          


  


        